OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779225068
OL,3,CBenefit cheat jailed for fraud after
OL,4,Cclaiming she could not walk after 10k
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FA woman who claimed she struggled to
OL,8,Fleave the house or walk has been
OL,9,Fjailed for benefit fraud after CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage showed her taking part in
OL,11,Fexercise classes at the gym.
OL,13,FHelen Green, 49, received more than
OL,14,F#25,000 in Personal Independence
OL,15,FPayment (PIP) between January 2020 and
OL,16,FMarch 2023. She told the Department
OL,17,Ffor Work and Pensions (DWP) she
OL,18,Fsuffered severe rheumatoid arthritis
OL,19,Fin every joint and a slipped disk that
OL,20,Fleft her housebound and in need of
OL,21,Fcrutches.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779225068
OL,3,CBenefit cheat jailed for fraud after
OL,4,Cclaiming she could not walk after 10k
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FGreen, from Shrewsbury, claimed her
OL,8,Farthritis was a lifelong condition
OL,9,Fthat would progressively get worse and
OL,10,Fsaid she could not walk for more than
OL,11,Ffive minutes without the use of
OL,12,Fcrutches.
OL,14,FShe also told the DWP she needed help
OL,15,Fwith washing, bathing, dressing,
OL,16,Fpreparing meals, eating and drinking.
OL,18,FA tip-off to the fraud line led to a
OL,19,FDWP investigation, which accused Green
OL,20,Fof falsely claiming #42,013 in PIP.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779225068
OL,3,CBenefit cheat jailed for fraud after
OL,4,Cclaiming she could not walk after 10k
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FThey discovered that Green regularly
OL,8,Fattended the gym, and was a member of
OL,9,Fa running club competing in 10k races,
OL,10,Fone of which she completed in an hour
OL,11,Fand three minutes.
OL,13,FShe was caught on security footage at
OL,14,Fthe gym taking part in Zumba, body
OL,15,Fcombat, body pump, core blast and spin
OL,16,Fclasses.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779225068
OL,3,CBenefit cheat jailed for fraud after
OL,4,Cclaiming she could not walk after 10k
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,FGreen pled guilty to dishonestly
OL,8,Ffailing to notify them of a change in
OL,9,Fcircumstances, and was jailed for
OL,10,Fseven months at Shrewsbury Crown Court
OL,11,Fon Tuesday (19 May).
OL,13,FMandy Tobias, from the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service, said: "Helen
OL,15,FGreen pretended she had limited
OL,16,Fmovement, but instead was a regular
OL,17,Frunner and active in gym classes.
OL,19,F"She did this for her own greed and
OL,20,Flined her pockets with fraudulently
OL,21,Fobtained money.
OL,26,@vD@\OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
