OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779225068
OL,3,CBenefit cheat jailed for fraud after
OL,4,Cclaiming she could not walk after 10k
OL,5,Crace
OL,7,F"The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,8,Fpresented strong evidence thanks to
OL,9,Fthe investigation work of the DWP
OL,10,Fshowing Green's deception, resulting
OL,11,Fin her guilty plea."
OL,13,FMinister for Transformation Andrew
OL,14,FWestern said Green's deception was a
OL,15,F"slap in the face to taxpayers" and
OL,16,Fthose who genuinely depend on PIP to
OL,17,Flive their lives.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@TO]wD@AOUwD@_O]
